<br>
They asked for a list.  Short and sweet.  If they want people who are vocal, jumping up and down waving their arms, crying like babies, flaming, etc.  They know where to go, the official vnboards at IGN are perfect for that.  <br>
<br>
All they are asking for is a succinct and detailed list of issues.  I think 3DKnight is doing a fine job of collecting and providing that information.  Pissing them off isn't going to help matters.  <br>
<br>
The fact they are even asking for a list shows that they are interested in making changes.<br>
<br>
